annotationA: Retina aberrant in pattern (Rap) binds to the Anaphase-Promoting Complex/Cyclosome (APC/C) ubiquitin ligase to stimulate its activity during G1 phase
annotationB: Imaginal discs arrested; Mitotic anaphase-promoting complex activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: imaginal disc development; positive regulation of mitotic metaphase/anaphase transition; regulation of cell cycle; neurogenesis; regulation of proteolysis
